# Add as GitHub Actions secrets (Settings → Secrets → Actions):
# GOOGLE_PLACES_API_KEY=your_google_api_key
#
# Recommended for numbered UK door addresses when typing a street name:
# GETADDRESS_DOMAIN_TOKEN=dtoken_...   (create at https://getaddress.io — restrict to your domain)
#
# In Google Cloud, restrict the key to HTTP referrers:
#   https://www.myairporttaxini.co.uk/*
#   https://myairporttaxini.co.uk/*
#
# Enable in Google Cloud (APIs & Services → Library):
#   - Places API (New)
# The route map uses OpenStreetMap and does not need Maps Embed API.

